Ericsson Media Solutions
gender pay gap report 
2017

Ericsson Internal  |  2018-02-21

Ensuring equality
At Ericsson, we work proactively 
to improve diversity and 
inclusion globally.
Our goal is to encourage a gender-intelligent 
organization which recognizes and values the 
differences that both men and women bring 
to the business. 
Over the past few years, Ericsson has made 
steady progress in increasing the number of 
women at senior-level positions. 

Ericsson Internal  |  2018-02-21

